to get us into the zone...

296
00:22:55,098 --> 00:22:58,124
and then we'll see if we can
scare up your missing spook.

297
00:22:58,234 --> 00:23:03,228
<i>Okay, clear your minds, which judging</i>
<i>by the looks of you, won't be that hard.</i>

298
00:23:03,339 --> 00:23:07,070
- Should we hold hands?
- Only if you're lonely.

299
00:23:07,176 --> 00:23:10,612
Now zip it,
and let me do my sweet funky.

300
00:23:10,713 --> 00:23:14,843
[Inhales Deeply, Exhales]

301
00:23:14,951 --> 00:23:20,253
I call upon the Guardian of Souls,
the Keeper of the Passage.

302
00:23:20,356 --> 00:23:24,793
Let our breath flow
from what is to what is past.

303
00:23:24,894 --> 00:23:27,988
Bless us with the presence of the lost.

304
00:23:28,097 --> 00:23:31,362
Grant us communion with
the world beyond our reach.

305
00:23:31,467 --> 00:23:35,301
Give voice to those
who can no longer be heard.

306
00:23:35,404 --> 00:23:40,137
I beseech you...
open your gates, reveal your secrets.

307
00:23:42,578 --> 00:23:45,411
