310
00:23:50,553 --> 00:23:53,716
- So much pain.
- He's in pain?

311
00:23:53,823 --> 00:23:57,281
<i>The dark soul.</i>
<i>So much suffering.</i>

312
00:23:57,393 --> 00:24:02,353
Dark, pain, suffering. They've got it.
Now, tell them to help me.

313
00:24:02,465 --> 00:24:05,229
It's coming.
It's coming.

314
00:24:05,334 --> 00:24:09,668
- I'm already here. What are you goin' on about?
<i>- Oh, God, I can feel it.</i>

315
00:24:09,772 --> 00:24:13,469
The dark soul.
It's here.

316
00:24:13,576 --> 00:24:17,205
It's... It's the...

317
00:24:17,313 --> 00:24:20,840
The Reaper!
