Bloody, but why would he go all scanners on her?

325
00:24:47,343 --> 00:24:51,837
He wouldn't. No advantage in it
to kill someone trying to help him.

326
00:24:51,948 --> 00:24:54,007
You saying it was an accident?

327
00:24:54,116 --> 00:24:57,882
Or whatever she contacted wasn't
the dark soul we were expecting.

328
00:24:57,987 --> 00:24:59,887
So if she wasn't
talking about Spike...

329
00:24:59,989 --> 00:25:03,823
