Reaper's supposed to
take souls, not make 'em.

334
00:26:01,150 --> 00:26:04,608
If it's come for me, couldn't have been
worried she was gonna help.

335
00:26:04,720 --> 00:26:07,348
She didn't even know I was there.

336
00:26:07,456 --> 00:26:09,686
Unless it wasn't about me.

337
00:26:12,428 --> 00:26:14,555
