338
00:26:14,664 --> 00:26:18,464
It was trying to hide something. Something
it didn't want you to know because...

339
00:26:28,945 --> 00:26:33,439
Come on.
Just reach out.

340
00:27:22,431 --> 00:27:24,490
Come on, then.
No more games.

341
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:27,398
No more hiding in the shadows.

342
00:27:27,503 --> 00:27:30,063
Let's do this,
right and proper.

343
00:27:30,172 --> 00:27:33,073
A lawyer?
[Chuckles]

344
00:27:37,079 --> 00:27:39,104
William.

345
00:27:44,687 --> 00:27:46,746
<i>- Please.</i>
- No.

346
00:27:49,125 --> 00:27:52,117
- It hurts.
- No!

347
00:27:52,228 --> 00:27:55,254
I'm not talking to flunkies anymore!
You hear that?

348
00:27:57,800 --> 00:28:00,860
Got your number, don't I? You're sending
