355
00:28:25,194 --> 00:28:28,994
But first, I get to play.

356
00:28:32,868 --> 00:28:35,029
Let's get started then...

357
00:28:37,273 --> 00:28:39,798
shall we?

358
00:28:43,679 --> 00:28:46,273
Got it.
The dark soul.

359
00:28:46,382 --> 00:28:48,942
- What's it say?
<i>- A lot.</i>

360
00:28:49,051 --> 00:28:51,349
