to get Spike back, before he's next.

400
00:31:01,517 --> 00:31:06,454
Vampire soul.
Watch it struggle.

401
00:31:06,555 --> 00:31:09,991
<i>- More fun than the others.</i>
- Go to hell.

402
00:31:14,029 --> 00:31:16,520
Your journey, not mine.

403
00:31:18,867 --> 00:31:22,963
Oh, the pretty.
Still trying to save you.

404
00:31:23,072 --> 00:31:25,836
Such passion.

405
00:31:25,941 --> 00:31:29,934
So wet and sweet.

406
00:31:30,045 --> 00:31:33,242
Perhaps I'll have a taste one day.

407
00:31:34,516 --> 00:31:36,609
[Chuckling]

408
00:31:36,719 --> 00:31:38,914
Still thinking like meat and bone.

409
00:31:39,021 --> 00:31:41,080
There's none here, boy.

410
00:31:41,190 --> 00:31:45,923
