all the rules are mine.

411
00:31:46,028 --> 00:31:50,021
<i>[Pavayne]</i>
<i>Reality bends. My desire.</i>

412
00:31:50,132 --> 00:31:53,033
<i>The way it was meant to.</i>

413
00:31:53,135 --> 00:31:55,103
Bending reality.

414
00:31:56,605 --> 00:31:59,904
