416
00:32:02,011 --> 00:32:05,708
<i>[Pavayne]</i>
<i>Parlor tricks, to amuse.</i>

417
00:32:05,814 --> 00:32:07,782
<i>Like your blood.</i>

418
00:32:12,955 --> 00:32:16,447
<i>Oh, yes.</i>
<i>Nothing here without the will.</i>

419
00:32:16,558 --> 00:32:20,585
<i>Your voice, your body...</i>

420
00:32:20,696 --> 00:32:23,631
<i>Clothes you think you wear.</i>

421
00:32:23,732 --> 00:32:27,896
<i>[Pavayne] William the Bloody.</i>
<i>Scourge and destroyer.</i>

422
00:32:28,003 --> 00:32:29,971
<i>But scratch the surface...</i>

423
00:32:30,072 --> 00:32:33,473
Little nancy, still crying
for his mother.

424
00:32:33,575 --> 00:32:36,806
<i>[Pavayne]</i>
<i>Know all your hiddens.</i>

425
00:32:36,912 --> 00:32:39,847
<i>Dirty red things you've done.</i>

426
00:32:39,948 --> 00:32:44,408
<i>Then fell in love,</i>
<i>won himself a soul.</i>

427
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:48,388
<i>No more dirty things.</i>
<i>Thinks himself special.</i>

428
00:32:48,490 --> 00:32:52,722
- Thinks it matters.
<i>- [Hanging Man] Hell still waits.</i>

429
00:32:52,828 --> 00:32:56,423
<i>[Pavayne]</i>
<i>Knows he deserves it like all the others.</i>

430
00:32:56,532 --> 00:32:58,830
- You killed them.
<i>- No.</i>

431
00:32:58,934 --> 00:33:03,633
<i>Died themselves.</i>
<i>Here, in service of Wolfram and Hart.</i>

432
00:33:03,739 --> 00:33:08,904
<i>Little ants,</i>
<i>scurrying from the flames.</i>

433
00:33:09,011 --> 00:33:14,881
Their spirits hung on. Tried to keep from
tumbling into hell. Until you gave them a shove.

434
00:33:14,983 --> 00:33:17,577
<i>[Pavayne]</i>
<i>Burning now.</i>

435
00:33:17,686 --> 00:33:21,782
<i>Screaming forever,</i>
<i>like you'll scream.</i>

436
00:33:21,890 --> 00:33:25,724
