be here then, can they?

437
00:33:27,162 --> 00:33:30,598
<i>[Spike]Just more of your tricks.</i>
<i>They aren't real.</i>

438
00:33:30,699 --> 00:33:34,396
<i>- [Pavayne] Real enough.</i>
- [Yells]

439
00:33:34,503 --> 00:33:38,701
<i>Hell always hungers</i>
<i>for the wicked, boy.</i>

440
00:33:38,807 --> 00:33:40,775
